Thoughts for statiscics
=======================


- Win/Loss Record: Total games won and lost. bar plot
- Average Points Per Game: Average points scored per game. number
- Consecutive Wins: Longest winning streak. number
- Ranking: Current ranking in the leaderboard. leaderboard ausschnitt mit highlighted rank
- Tournaments Won: Number of tournaments won. number
- Best Finish: Highest position achieved in a tournament. number
- Points Scored: Total points scored across all games. number
- Performance Over Time: Graphs showing improvement or decline in performance. graph

Visualizations: Use graphs, charts, and heatmaps to visualize data effectively.
Real-Time Updates: Provide real-time updates to keep the statistics current.
